<!DOCTYPE html>
<html style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <title>The Digital Heir - Email Verification</title>

    <style type="text/css">
        img {
            max-width: 100%;
        }
        body {
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;
            width: 100% !important;
            height: 100%;
            line-height: 1.6em;
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 640px) {
            body {
                padding: 0 !important;
            }
            h1 {
                font-weight: 800 !important;
                margin: 20px 0 5px !important;
            }
            h2 {
                font-weight: 800 !important;
                margin: 20px 0 5px !important;
            }
            .container {
                padding: 0 !important;
                width: 100% !important;
            }
            .content-wrap {
                padding: 10px !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/EmailMessage" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; width: 100% !important; height: 100%; line-height: 1.6em; background-color: #f6f6f6; margin: 0;" bgcolor="#f6f6f6">
<table class="body-wrap" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; width: 100%; background-color: #f6f6f6; margin: 0;" bgcolor="#f6f6f6">
    <tr>
        <td></td>
        <td class="container" width="600" style="display: block !important; max-width: 600px !important; margin: 0 auto;">
            <div class="content" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
                <table class="main" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-radius: 3px; background-color: #fff; border: 1px solid #e9e9e9;" bgcolor="#fff">
                    <tr>
                        <td class="content-wrap" style="padding: 20px;">
                            <!-- Logo and Title Section -->
                            <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                                <a href="https://thedigitalheir.com/">
                                    <img src="https://thedigitalheir.com/build/android-chrome-192x192.png" alt="The Digital Heir Logo" style="max-width: 120px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                                </a>
                                <p style="margin: 5px 0 15px; font-size: 16px; color: #666;">The Eternity</p>
                                <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #333;">The Digital Heir</h1>

                            </div>
                            <!-- Email Text Section -->
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">

                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 0 0 20px;">
                                        Hey {{ beneficiaryFullName }},  A person named {{ customerFullName }} has listed this contact ({{ emailAddress }}) as an emergency contact on  <a href="https://thedigitalheir.com/">The Digital Heir</a>.
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 0 0 20px;">
                                        He has left a Secure Envelope for you, encoded with an answer to a private question. You can attempt to decrypt it by following the button below.
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 0 0 20px;">
                                        This link has been generated specifically for you and will expire in one week. The same link with a similar message will also be sent to other contacts designated by {{ customerFullName }} as yours.
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 0 0 20px; text-align: center;">
                                        <a href="{{ accessUrl }}" class="btn-primary" style="color: #FFF; text-decoration: none; line-height: 2em; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; border-radius: 5px; background-color: #348eda; padding: 10px 20px; border: 1px solid #348eda;">Open Secret Envelope</a>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 0 0 20px;">
                                        If this was a mistake, no action is needed â€” you will not receive further emails from us. However, you can still unsubscribe using the link below.
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 0 0 20px;">
                                        &mdash; The Digital Heir
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
                <div class="footer" style="text-align: center; color: #999; padding: 20px; font-size: 12px;">
                    &copy; {{ year }} The Digital Heir. All rights reserved.
                </div>
            </div>
        </td>
        <td></td>
    </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>